Reasoning: The paper discusses a numerical solution method for hyperbolic partial differential equations using Spacetime Discontinuous Galerkin finite element methods. This involves constructing an unstructured simplicial spacetime mesh over an arbitrary simplicial space domain. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.NA (Numerical Analysis). Other likely sub-categories include cs.MS (Mathematical Software), cs.CE (Computational Engineering), cs.CG (Computational Geometry), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
